  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK997">
<l>arampōluṅ kūrmaiya rēṉu marampōlvar</l>
<l>makkaṭpaṇ pillā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who is destitute of (true) human qualities (only) resembles a tree, though he may possess the sharpness of a file.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
